I was?

11
00:00:59,458 --> 00:01:00,832
Very affectionate.

12
00:01:00,999 --> 00:01:04,123
I remember nothing.
You must have been dreaming.

13
00:01:04,874 --> 00:01:07,582
We were both wide awake, and you know it.

14
00:01:07,749 --> 00:01:10,332
Then I yielded to temptation.

15
00:01:10,499 --> 00:01:12,415
It's the last time.

16
00:01:12,583 --> 00:01:13,832
It is?

17
00:01:13,999 --> 00:01:16,998
As of today, I'm on the road to chastity.

18
00:01:17,499 --> 00:01:20,665
Come now. I liked you better last night.

19
00:01:20,833 --> 00:01:22,582
Last night was last night!

20
00:01:45,874 --> 00:01:50,832
LOVE ON THE RUN

21
